{"tid":168413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【屬於香港中學生的籃球主題曲】告別球場時","createTime":"2017-03-23T13:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T12:35:15.000Z","uid":47374,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d423e04d45c272a7f929f76037df6b892d31e9a","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/23/214509_3cb7a93323960d3d991182d4367d9d62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F214509_3cb7a93323960d3d991182d4367d9d62.jpg&h=84ea2f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1825606591025644/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1825606591025644%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=902a4532\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1825606591025644/</a><br />\n<br />\n誠意送呢首歌比所有讀過中學嘅香港人<br />\n想提提大家，中學?波友必定會愈來愈少<br />\n趁後生儲多啲回憶，將來無人嚟打波時，諗返當打咗<br />\n<br />\n歡迎tag大家tag波友，我IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Frealbasketballcoach%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=77447f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n原：告別校園(李克勤)<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：Adrian Tang<br />\n<br />\n呢班Form1 相約落堂後較量<br />\n三點半 個個掛住落場<br />\n一班friend 恤衫上陣狂扮偶像<br />\n高比呀 你點解偏要硬上<br />\n<br />\n中三參加班際實情係無壞<br />\n加油呀 睇班長沙聲都嗌<br />\n一招拉桿吸引十零件少艾<br />\n叻仔喇 你應該打下學界<br />\n<br />\n有勁人 有高佬 狂block你 五六球<br />\n有隊形 又有種 係堅揪<br />\n有熱情 有粗口 場波至 有汗流<br />\n球場上永遠有個光陰小偷<br />\n<br />\nOOH 劉華問我<br />\n返工點樣鬥波 唔做會餓<br />\nOOH 從前隊友<br />\n今晚好想鬥波 求其嚟六個 OOh...<br />\n<br />\n個罰球 你air咗 唔緊要 有下球<br />\n發現同學笑聲 未識收<br />\n到下球 你air咗 人生再 無下球<br />\n球場大笑嘅只得光陰小偷<br />\n<br />\nOOH 黎明問我<br />\n新婚點樣鬥波 忙住慶賀<br />\n<br />\nOOH 肥城問我<br />\n生?仔點鬥波 唔嚟唔係錯<br />\n<br />\nOOH 陳年學友<br />\n七張幾點鬥波 無謂惹禍<br />\n<br />\nOOH 從前隊友<br />\n今晚好想鬥波 全場嚟十個"},{"pid":"2d5e0465064cd71b5ce01596ea0c21522e97bfc4","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"自堆"},{"pid":"dbda52b9bd1587234cfb1be9706e5d8294593a3f","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b5926117295b4f73229120981f00fc8dc22cdd05","tid":168413,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\nbtw見到我母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dd790ab94fda1a82fddbd0f2a67f585ca6910e","tid":168413,"uid":62555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"好想打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d46ab2195b507ad7252ea1c61e90568035bd24","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<br />\n<br />\nbtw見到我母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪英華"},{"pid":"a745a31acc51f580f61192209648556b76685a05","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲波友唔見晒未"},{"pid":"35a923e1c482231a6a0e285c41f69ceaa41ace86","tid":168413,"uid":62555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好想打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲波友唔見晒未</blockquote><br />\n無左好耐"},{"pid":"bc0ec177d5344e60ce58708c9ae5e2afafbdf496","tid":168413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:38:32.0